item.title: T3-Paper-Code
item.description: Observations on Every Third Digit of the Thue-Morse Sequence # Adam Hutchings | Henry Hutchings | Jake Roggenbuck Abstract # We investigate some interesting properties of the sequence made up of every third term of the Thue-Morse sequence, and consider other similar sequences.
